title: Computer tomography scanner density by country 2017
summary: This is a bar chart representing Country in the x axis and CT scanners per million population in the y axis.
The CT scanners per million population is highest at Country Australia and lowest at Country Mexico.
The difference of CT scanners per million population between the highest and lowest Country is 58.23.
